{"tid":449762,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"(有冇同好!!)Nowhere boys!!","createTime":"2017-10-27T13:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T16:08:33.000Z","uid":47123,"like":16,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"88802a75c1a42a0fb7fc46b4aa4d418d254ff2f4","tid":449762,"uid":47123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"唔好急住負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽下佢地啲歌先喇<br />\nNowhere Boys名字來自關於約翰藍儂成長的電影「Nowhere Boy」，當中有一幕提到他曾被學校老師潑冷水，對他說「You're going nowhere.」，但他的回應竟是「Is nowhere full of geniuses, sir?」。樂隊成員都是披頭四樂團超級粉絲，仰慕約翰藍儂的率性，也想到達「full of geniuses」的音樂國度。<br />\n樂隊成員包括<br />\n主音Van Chan<br />\n鼓手Nate Wong<br />\n吉他手Kenneth Angus<br />\n鍵琴手／小提琴手Fisher Kan(漁佬)<br />\n低音吉他手Hansun Chan。<br />\n樂隊將他們的音樂稱為Cinematic Rock (電影式搖滾)。Nowhere Boys大部份的歌曲都啟發自電影<br />\n(源自維基）<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/Nowhere_boys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2FNowhere_boys&d=jIL39pIbFOF4JYuFmENEzTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7bd6a228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/Nowhere_boys</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/27/210255_60dc54ecedbdc2e16f4abc473a329d1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2F210255_60dc54ecedbdc2e16f4abc473a329d1e.jpg&h=383ce4c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/27/210257_87a1968aac5e21a6a641887e6832273a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2F210257_87a1968aac5e21a6a641887e6832273a.jpg&h=e36cc18d&s={SIZE}\" />。<br />\n<br />\n佢地今晚有音樂會 但係去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好後悔<br />\n好彩有直播可以慢慢j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be9682fb271f619b5a39fe995afe837a09cce70","tid":449762,"uid":89235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"去咗！比想像中正好多！細場睇band show係爽嘅，不過人數比想像少..."},{"pid":"35b038a0a8c43cbb9a9b7d44aa43669ab7df6e84","tid":449762,"uid":128760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T16:26:05.000Z","msg":"去咗"},{"pid":"f2cdc3633c8d8ec45b04227af9f5753b09ea722e","tid":449762,"uid":122572,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T17:14:12.000Z","msg":"正呀<br />\n現場音響算set得唔錯<br />\n但supper出尼就炒埋哂一碟咁<br />\njing都彈埋結他就正<br />\n中段靜嗰part少少改編都做得幾有心思<br />\n係阿ken炒粉明顯左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出哂三隻碟嘅歌<br />\n總體都值得讚<br />\n人數少就預左<br />\n見到眾籌個進度都比想像中慢"},{"pid":"e1445f2462de1a3d407f3fc2e0d353d4e646cd99","tid":449762,"uid":27071,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T17:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾屎就收皮啦"},{"pid":"78dc276ccde1b7878ea17cf864ff7ff3b1ae68b7","tid":449762,"uid":122572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T01:02:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84bb67c03af197bd02010efc08a1396817311edd","tid":449762,"uid":47123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T05:57:51.000Z","msg":"想買地心吸力tee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a70f3624f9cc83e3cd1cfcab4205fc52c171cf1","tid":449762,"uid":47123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T05:59:37.000Z","msg":"第一次聽地心吸力覺得好奇怪 聽多幾次就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489762fcd06f5c3dd81cd295247c5c5cd107860d","tid":449762,"uid":47123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:02:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去咗！比想像中正好多！細場睇band show係爽嘅，不過人數比想像少...</blockquote><br />\n想由頭追一隊band<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由冇人識到慢慢有人知 由細場慢慢變大場 好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"